_sText:
I created this map for fun, yes it is orange, yes it is because I'm lazy.
It is also because I believe orange maps can look good as any other maps can and the gameplay matters more in that kind of map.
In this map you can see the logo of the gaming community Howned.com, it's a french gaming community (mostly Counter Strike Source) and if you speak French I really advise you to come play with us!

Oh and I almost forgot, There are a few secrets in this map, will you find them all?

_**EDIT: Please rate my map and/or leave a comment, I'd like to know what you like and dislike about it so I can improve myself before starting a new one :)**_
